{"tid":553594,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"整過中文輸入法既麻煩入一入 有野請教","createTime":"2018-02-07T15:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T15:17:14.000Z","uid":38256,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"14aea69a233bf23310237f2e759c72be2ea9118f","tid":553594,"uid":38256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"小弟想整個iOS 即時翻譯既keyboard<br />\n因為自己英文差成日要查字 <br />\n平日個流程系 <strong>用緊Whatsapp想翻譯 -&gt; 開Google translate 查 -&gt; 複製個解釋 -&gt; 開番Whatsapp -&gt; 貼上</strong><br />\n要常常來回兩只Apps 十分不方便 <br />\n但搵過Apps store都無一只可以做到即時翻譯既keyboard 所以想自己整<br />\n期望個流程系 系Whatsapp 用自制個keyboard 輸入中文/英文 -&gt; 自動send 上 Google translate api 或 Microsoft Translator Text API -&gt; keyboard上方會顯示翻譯 -&gt; 點擊文字 會將翻譯填入輸入框<br />\n<br />\n初步理解中文輸入法既原理係好似查字典咁樣<br />\n首先有個cin檔（字典）<br />\n根據用家的輸入做filter<br />\n<br />\n例如 &quot;登&quot; 速成碼系弓廿 n=弓 t=廿<br />\n之後在速成的cin檔 search &quot;nt&quot; 就會出現&quot;登&quot;  *見圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/231012_5ab3f7119a0d80044139dd77d71bea5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F231012_5ab3f7119a0d80044139dd77d71bea5e.png&h=52c754ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我遇到第一個難題就系<br />\n我平時手機同電腦都係用筆劃輸入法, 所以都想個keyboard支援<br />\n我已經在 <a href=\"https://github.com/chinese-opendesktop/cin-tables\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fchinese-opendesktop%2Fcin-tables&d=voCK8FXwRRmMHUQ%2Fw2iICMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a0c6766f\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/chinese-opendesktop/cin-tables</a> 搵到很多中文輸入法的cin檔（速成,倉頡等）<br />\n但係就係搵唔到<strong><em>筆劃輸入法</em></strong>的cin檔<br />\n注意⚠️ 不是 筆順 五筆 六筆 輸入法  <br />\n*筆劃輸入法示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/232329_3d4de79b8d2c2c142325f23f61c98d3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F232329_3d4de79b8d2c2c142325f23f61c98d3b.png&h=71d8abde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特意上來求助 希望有大神可以提供<strong><em>筆劃輸入法</em></strong> 的cin檔 或 給點建議<br />\n麻煩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27cc25d984513096abe2f0491c6f172e5188321","tid":553594,"uid":51319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fd0c1bc5ea5bbe5fbe728513420990656f515c","tid":553594,"uid":51319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c47bc7a74bdd45139f9f570fbe8b9d7e91c6769","tid":553594,"uid":88859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38306fb1dadd35561f1d945f4ca42e77140b723","tid":553594,"uid":51319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9890e9bb6c6a6d4d82c2f732da9f7e66f122319b","tid":553594,"uid":36478,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aea69a233bf23310237f2e759c72be2ea9118f","tid":553594,"uid":38256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"小弟想整個iOS 即時翻譯既keyboard<br />\n因為自己英文差成日要查字 <br />\n平日個流程系 <strong>用緊Whatsapp想翻譯 -&gt; 開Google translate 查 -&gt; 複製個解釋 -&gt; 開番Whatsapp -&gt; 貼上</strong><br />\n要常常來回兩只Apps 十分不方便 <br />\n但搵過Apps store都無一只可以做到即時翻譯既keyboard 所以想自己整<br />\n期望個流程系 系Whatsapp 用自制個keyboard 輸入中文/英文 -&gt; 自動send 上 Google translate api 或 Microsoft Translator Text API -&gt; keyboard上方會顯示翻譯 -&gt; 點擊文字 會將翻譯填入輸入框<br />\n<br />\n初步理解中文輸入法既原理係好似查字典咁樣<br />\n首先有個cin檔（字典）<br />\n根據用家的輸入做filter<br />\n<br />\n例如 &quot;登&quot; 速成碼系弓廿 n=弓 t=廿<br />\n之後在速成的cin檔 search &quot;nt&quot; 就會出現&quot;